Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.57,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Acesta e palatul din Idanokan?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.11,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Were we able to make it back?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.11,0:00:20.66,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,It's so dark, I can hardly see.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.02,0:00:24.95,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Amber?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.36,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,There are no monsters nearby.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.83,0:00:34.76,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,There's nothing living, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.39,0:00:37.14,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Are you feeling sad?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.71,0:00:41.08,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.18,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,I smell blood.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.18,Dialogue,Group,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.01,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,I'm blinded!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.85,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,Is this better?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.85,0:00:54.54,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.31,0:01:12.10,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,This armor... belongs to imperial soldiers.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.55,0:01:14.85,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,They must have fought the monsters here.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.47,0:01:18.36,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,They couldn't even bury their dead?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.85,0:01:20.94,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Just how intense was the fighting?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.43,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,It's possible this world is already...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.37,0:01:30.26,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.12,Dialogue,Soldier,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.42,0:01:42.82,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,The Imperial Army!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.12,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,There are some still engaged in combat?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.79,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou, over there!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.01,0:01:49.14,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.01,0:01:51.75,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.10,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.19,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,The Abyss King.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.59,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,If you go down through here, you'll come out \Non the flank of the monster horde.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.28,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,You'll be able to catch \Nthe Abyss King by surprise.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.28,0:03:52.94,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.72,0:03:54.99,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.09,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.06,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,We have all the rings.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.09,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I have everyone's power.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.92,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,This is sooner than we expected,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.02,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,but this is what we returned home for.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.55,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Please, Ring King.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.60,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,I'm betting everything on you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.99,0:04:18.07,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be fine, Satou-sama.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.07,0:04:18.86,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.10,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Ring King.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.69,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.49,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting, okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.97,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.77,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.91,Dialogue,AbyssKing,0,0,0,,You're here,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.56,Dialogue,AbyssKing,0,0,0,,Inheritor of the Rings?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.73,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,You've done well to make it this far.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.61,0:05:41.47,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,Boy, new King,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.25,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,I'll unite your power.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.89,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.06,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,This time, hold nothing back.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.61,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.06,0:06:58.95,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.67,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.71,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.35,0:07:12.74,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,The Rings are the manifestation \Nof the world's order.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.25,0:07:15.88,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,The Abyss is supposed to perish,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.50,Dialogue,Ring,0,0,0,,and the world is supposed to be saved...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.46,0:07:25.63,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Does this mean... I'm not good enough?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.80,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.72,Dialogue,AbyssKing,0,0,0,,Inheritor of the Rings.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.40,0:07:37.09,Dialogue,AbyssKing,0,0,0,,So, you are another ignorant puppet?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.96,0:07:38.85,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.27,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.66,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,What about our duty?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.66,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,What happened to the legends?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.99,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.57,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,We can't afford to lose Satou here!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.87,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.95,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,I won't let him die.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.15,0:08:12.09,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,So, it really is possible to be unable \Nto move a single finger...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.35,Dialogue,AbyssKing,0,0,0,,Return to the Abyss.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.79,Dialogue,AbyssKing,0,0,0,,Women of the Rings...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.97,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Everyone? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.84,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,You think we'd just abandon you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Granart!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.63,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Damn it! Let me go!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.85,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Tsk! There are too many.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.09,0:10:02.91,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.04,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,Satou-sama!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.61,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.61,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.79,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Satou!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.04,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Hime!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.25,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Good morning, Satou.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.81,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Hime...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.89,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.27,0:11:00.59,Dialogue,Priest,0,0,0,,Do you promise to love and to cherish \None another, in sickness and in health?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.13,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.21,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.99,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,You're awake, Satou-kun?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.06,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Oh... I guess I died?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.03,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.27,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,We haven't died yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.02,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.93,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Alabaster-dono saved us.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.30,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,That's the Great Sage for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.16,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.26,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I'm not that great.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Creating an opening and getting \Nyou all away from the Abyss King
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.05,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,was the best I could manage.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.51,0:12:40.27,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,We really do need the\N Ring King's power, after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.69,0:12:45.16,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! If you're safe, \Nthen that means Marse-san is...!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.82,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Prince Marse is safe, too, yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.35,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to this one.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.75,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.27,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Ring King.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.68,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,I'm from Wind's royal family of Romca,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.92,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,Smaragdi Romca.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.11,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Thanks to Smaragdi,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.11,0:13:14.23,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,we managed to escape from \Nthe Abyss Monsters that surrounded us.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.33,0:13:19.65,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,I've been watching over \NAlabaster-sama for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.81,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,However, once he was faced with danger...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.79,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,I couldn't sit still.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.57,0:13:30.89,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,Because of that, \NI was able to aid Alabaster-sama.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.89,0:13:36.40,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,Alabaster-sama gave my life \Nsuch wonderful meaning.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.79,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,To me, he truly is my one...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.50,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,The monsters have withdrawn.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.50,0:13:50.10,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I believe the Abyss King \Nhas suffered a serious wound, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.52,0:13:53.60,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I guess I at least had some effect.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.31,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.79,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,It was wonderfully effective.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.79,0:14:02.44,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,We couldn't even get \Na single arrow to pierce him.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.04,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,You've done well, Satou-kun.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.98,0:14:12.66,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Great Sage, what is the overall situation like?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.96,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Shortly after you left,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.96,0:14:19.15,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,the Abyss King's forces \Ncommenced their invasion,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.15,0:14:23.66,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,and the Imperial Army halted their advance \Nat the Great Mountain Wall.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.56,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I assisted, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.38,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,there was little we could do \Nother than run away.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.66,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,And Maasa?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.35,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,What happened to Maasa?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:32.73,0:14:37.42,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Each nation is fighting in different locations.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.50,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Maasa is safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.50,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Prince Marse is there, as well.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.77,0:14:48.41,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Though the number of monsters \Njust keeps going up, not down.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.91,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,The situation is steadily worsening.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.33,0:14:55.12,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I'm really glad we didn't give up hope.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.60,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all made it back!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.40,0:15:02.33,Dialogue,Smaragdi,0,0,0,,Alabaster-sama, it's almost dawn.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.05,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,The Ring King has returned.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.76,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,All the princesses are together, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.04,0:15:11.79,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,The morning sun is full of hope.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.20,Dialogue,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Ring King has returned!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.38,Dialogue,Citizen,0,0,0,,All five princesses are with him!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.98,Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,I was told I couldn't go outside \Nbecause there's lots of monsters.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.98,0:15:34.28,Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,But it'll be okay now that \Nyou're back, right, Ring King?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.91,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.25,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,I'll save this world!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:44.10,0:15:48.65,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Now, we need to talk about what's to come.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.65,0:15:52.38,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Before that, I'd like to hear your excuse.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.09,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,I thought we were supposed \Nto be able to defeat the Abyss King
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.22,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,once the Rings were collected?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.89,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Grandpa, be honest with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.44,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Was my power not enough?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.80,0:16:11.57,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I have one idea as to why you \Nweren't able to defeat the Abyss King.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:12.02,0:16:19.40,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,There was not one mention of \Nthe Black Rings that the Abyss King wore.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.37,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,Black Rings?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.92,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,They looked just like this, only black.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.13,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,That's not in my records.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.01,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,The dwarves didn't know about that, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.66,0:16:34.01,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Still, even in multiple sources,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.01,0:16:38.35,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,it's certain that the Ring King \Nsealed away the Abyss King.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.35,0:16:43.85,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,However, we don't know how much \Npower was required to do so.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.29,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Then what are you saying we should do?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.65,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,There's only one thing we can do.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:49.16,0:16:53.74,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,We have to draw out even more of \Nthe Rings' power before our next battle!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.74,0:16:59.12,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Which means Satou-kun needs to strengthen his\Nbonds with the Ring Princesses even further.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.37,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Even stronger bonds... Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.68,0:17:03.98,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Baby making!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.53,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Well, that's one option.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.79,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,It is?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.63,Dialogue,Marse,0,0,0,,Satou-kun!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.02,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Marse-san!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.17,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.84,Dialogue,Marse,0,0,0,,I received word that you \Nhad returned, and came at once.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.98,Dialogue,Marse,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.45,0:17:24.77,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Now, moving on to the main topic.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.89,0:17:32.54,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,It's said that the Ring Princesses stood \Nalongside the Ring King in battle long ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.93,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,In order to draw out the Rings' power,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.28,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,both the will to fight alongside him
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.28,0:17:43.54,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,and the strength to carry out \Nthat will may be required.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.11,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Strength, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.50,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Saphir, Amber, and I may be fine there...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.80,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,But we're not very helpful.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.09,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,So, on that note,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.43,0:17:57.55,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,we'll have everyone acquire the strength \Nthat befits a wife of the Ring King!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.89,0:18:01.76,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,That's right, this training...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.15,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,is wife training!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.86,Dialogue,Maid,0,0,0,,This will be your room, Ring King.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.58,Dialogue,Maid,0,0,0,,The Princesses are already waiting for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.77,0:18:34.88,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Satou, once again, you made up your mind \Nto fight to save this world for our sakes.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.84,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,So I believe we should \Nsteel our resolve, as well.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.93,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,Ring King, replenish your energy \Nas much as you need.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.77,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Now, choose the woman you'd like!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.64,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,Of course, you're welcome \Nto choose all of us at once!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.06,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.92,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NIsn't a harem every man's dream?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.92,0:18:57.82,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Look at what you're doing. \NYou're troubling the Ring King.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.53,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,This is the problem with beastmen \Nwho can't read the mood.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.78,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.02,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.77,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,That's big talk from the shorty \Nwho fell behind her little sister!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.65,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,Huh?! Saphira has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.75,0:19:13.18,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,{\an8}What? Did I hit the mark? \NYou're raising your voice so much.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.62,Dialogue,Saphir,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.05,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Bridal training, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.10,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,You sound happy.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.73,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Huh? Not particularly.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.18,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,You've been working \Nso hard for us this whole time,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.14,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,so it's my turn to work hard, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.78,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.50,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.48,0:19:48.95,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,In my real family, I had a father, \Na mother, and a little sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:49.83,0:19:52.37,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,My little sister remained in this world,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.82,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,so I haven't seen her in ten years now.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.49,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,My parents are here.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:59.99,0:20:04.42,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Father, Mother, I'm home.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.02,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,It happened when I was little.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.14,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,So I only vaguely remember \Nwhat they looked like,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:10.76,0:20:15.22,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,but they both risked their lives to protect me.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.99,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,This man...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.55,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,is my husband.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.83,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Thank you, Satou.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:28.77,0:20:32.60,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,I was able to return here, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.67,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,Krystal.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.21,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Grandpa?! How long have you been there?!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.52,Dialogue,Amber,0,0,0,,Since, "Father, Mother, I'm home."
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.01,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,That's basically the whole time!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.38,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,I don't think it's anything \Nto be embarrassed about.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.38,0:20:52.53,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,I think it was a lovely story.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.13,0:20:56.85,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,By the way, about your magic training.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.33,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.36,Dialogue,Hime,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.36,0:21:02.30,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,No, it won't be me.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.20,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I've summoned a teacher \Nmore appropriate for you, Krystal.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:06.86,0:21:10.53,Dialogue,Alabaster,0,0,0,,I wanted to let you know,\N since they should be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.90,0:21:14.87,Dialogue,Granart,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.45,0:21:31.14,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,Hmm, so you're...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:31.57,0:21:33.32,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,You're not too bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.77,0:21:42.13,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,I'm Morion Ravri Nokanatika.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.81,0:21:45.03,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,Mă bucur să te văd,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.44,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,surioară.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.87,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,Și...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.47,Dialogue,Morion,0,0,0,,Cumnate.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.91,Dialogue,Nef,0,0,0,,Cumnat?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.62,0:21:59.65,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Morion Ravri Nokanatika?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.69,Dialogue,Satou,0,0,0,,Tu ești sora mai mică a lui Hime?!
